language provides no way to directly exercise [[Delete]], the tests are placed here.
tests.description: delete operator throws TypeError when deleting a non-configurable data property in strict mode

Strict Mode - SyntaxError is thrown for --arguments
Strict Mode - SyntaxError is throw if the UnaryExpression operated upon by a Prefix Increment operator(--arguments)
Strict Mode - SyntaxError is not thrown for --arguments[...]
